{"id":835955230,"question_id":264,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 7 months","timestamp":1667466416,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"164 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/835955230/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Ugly Number II","memory":"53.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\n   public int nthUglyNumber(int n) {\n        if(n==1) return 1;\n       \n        PriorityQueue<Long> q = new PriorityQueue();\n        q.add(1l);\n\n        for(long i=1; i<n; i++) {\n            long tmp = q.poll();\n            while(!q.isEmpty() && q.peek()==tmp) tmp = q.poll();\n\n            q.add(tmp*2);\n            q.add(tmp*3);\n            q.add(tmp*5);\n        }\n        return q.poll().intValue();\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"ugly-number-ii","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
